author: Maria Mellor, WIRED UK
title: Coronavirus Has Created a Sex Boom—but Maybe Not a Baby Boom
description: Isolated couples are purchasing toys by the bucketload, and activity on dating apps is way up. But more babies might not be on the way.
content:
The clubs are shut. The pubs are shut. Tinder dates are canceled. One-night stands are practically illegal. But, despite these obvious hurdles, coronavirus has still created a sex industry sales boom. 
This story originally appeared on WIRED UK.
